# rosetta-frida pre-push hook — the full CI mirror.
#
# Runs `npm run verify`: typecheck + lint (repo-wide) + format:check
# + the full test suite with the 100% coverage gate. This is exactly
# what GitHub Actions runs, so a green pre-push is a green CI.
#
# Pre-commit only lints the staged files (via lint-staged) for speed —
# this hook catches:
#   - typecheck failures
#   - lint regressions in files you DIDN'T touch this commit
#   - format drift outside your staged set
#   - test failures or coverage drops
#
# Bypass with `git push --no-verify` for WIP branches. Discouraged on
# master.
npm run verify
